    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=607984656221995780&sectionId=607988888157291418)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDSW0LK1i_text","label":"ggvDSW0LK1i_text","default":"<strong>THE NIGHT EVERYTHING CHANGED...</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkDJexj3CO_youtubeUrl","label":"ggkDJexj3CO_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkDJexj3CO_vimeoUrl","label":"ggkDJexj3CO_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/1095883398"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkDJexj3CO_html5Url","label":"ggkDJexj3CO_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/79a13245cb204f65888a6cb1e3bac7ca.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJUPHzo7jr_text","label":"ggJUPHzo7jr_text","default":"For the next 3 months, I lived like a man possessed."},{"type":"html","id":"gg8LneBLODQ_text","label":"gg8LneBLODQ_text","default":"I devoured every study. Called researchers in Japan who'd been studying microcirculation for decades. Flew to a conference in Sweden on regenerative therapy. Spent $28,000 of our savings on medical journals and insider reports."},{"type":"html","id":"ggrKtw1ODlk_text","label":"ggrKtw1ODlk_text","default":"And what I found made me want to punch a hole through my computer screen."},{"type":"html","id":"gg4bn5Tc4nQ_text","label":"gg4bn5Tc4nQ_text","default":"<strong>The entire shoulder invasive procedures industry is built on a lie.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRlgREZ1W9_text","label":"ggRlgREZ1W9_text","default":"A $73 billion dollar lie that keeps you sick, desperate, and reaching for your wallet."},{"type":"html","id":"gg5i3YyB_yE_text","label":"gg5i3YyB_yE_text","default":"Here's what they don't want you to know:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggja8pjfgFO_text","label":"ggja8pjfgFO_text","default":"<strong>87% of chronic rotator cuff pain has NOTHING to do with the tear itself.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg37aKfTxdj_text","label":"gg37aKfTxdj_text","default":"It's not about \"strengthening the muscles.\" It's not about \"improving range of motion.\" It's not about \"reducing inflammation.\""},{"type":"html","id":"ggDlvX1n6r2_text","label":"ggDlvX1n6r2_text","default":"That's why none of the methods I tried ever worked."},{"type":"html","id":"ggEBDu_DApZ_text","label":"ggEBDu_DApZ_text","default":"The REAL cause is something so simple, so obvious, that I kicked myself for missing it all these years."},{"type":"html","id":"ggMxhVqaF4x_text","label":"ggMxhVqaF4x_text","default":"<strong>Your shoulder tissue is literally suffocating.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrfmxy_diR_text","label":"ggrfmxy_diR_text","default":"Let me explain..."},{"type":"html","id":"ggWMEp8PDJa_text","label":"ggWMEp8PDJa_text","default":"<strong>THE NIGHT EVERYTHING CHANGED...</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeNIgKSm5n_youtubeUrl","label":"ggeNIgKSm5n_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeNIgKSm5n_vimeoUrl","label":"ggeNIgKSm5n_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/1095883398"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeNIgKSm5n_html5Url","label":"ggeNIgKSm5n_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/6cf6e2e1b1ba4cd184a85f517e553c26.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWWbe2Zc_3_text","label":"ggWWbe2Zc_3_text","default":"Think of your shoulder like a door hinge."},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ05_Mc4h2_text","label":"ggJ05_Mc4h2_text","default":"When you're young, your shoulder moves like a brand-new hinge - smooth, silent, effortless."},{"type":"html","id":"gge5Ut6czwF_text","label":"gge5Ut6czwF_text","default":"That's because it's constantly bathed in nutrient-rich blood. Like a perfectly oiled hinge that glides without friction."},{"type":"html","id":"gg8zFqw2xpb_text","label":"gg8zFqw2xpb_text","default":"But here's what happens after age 40..."},{"type":"html","id":"gggD89nLPUq_text","label":"gggD89nLPUq_text","default":"The blood supply starts drying up. The vessels disappear. The tissue starves."},{"type":"html","id":"ggo0lOV_Evo_text","label":"ggo0lOV_Evo_text","default":"Your shoulder starts moving like an old, rusty hinge that hasn't been oiled in years."},{"type":"html","id":"ggQK1WMEPYv_text","label":"ggQK1WMEPYv_text","default":"You know the sound - that grinding, creaking protest every time it moves."},{"type":"html","id":"ggAGoueEARl_childItem_0","label":"ggAGoueEARl_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>By 50,</strong> you've lost 50% of circulation. Your hinge is starting to creak.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAGoueEARl_childItem_1","label":"ggAGoueEARl_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>By 60,</strong> it&#039;s 70% gone. Now it&#039;s grinding, sticking, protesting with every movement.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggI9Hxv98Ui_text","label":"ggI9Hxv98Ui_text","default":"You feel it in the morning stiffness. The catching sensation when you reach overhead. The way your shoulder \"talks to you\" throughout the day."},{"type":"html","id":"gg9JtbGisuc_text","label":"gg9JtbGisuc_text","default":"Your shoulder tissue is literally dying from lack of oxygen and nutrients."},{"type":"html","id":"gggIIfr1wfo_text","label":"gggIIfr1wfo_text","default":"Like that rusty hinge slowly seizing up, metal grinding against metal, wearing itself down with every movement."},{"type":"html","id":"gg77a97fxor_text","label":"gg77a97fxor_text","default":"<strong>The medical industry KNOWS this.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggs6B3fbGNy_text","label":"ggs6B3fbGNy_text","default":"They've known it since 1987 when Japanese researcher Dr. Hideki Matsumoto proved that 91% of failed shoulder surgeries had one thing in common: <strong>severely compromised blood flow.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtD9pP8kIw_text","label":"ggtD9pP8kIw_text","default":"But here's the kicker..."},{"type":"html","id":"gg40kG5o1eI_text","label":"gg40kG5o1eI_text","default":"<strong>There's no money in addressing it.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8RQANbqEx_text","label":"gg8RQANbqEx_text","default":"Why?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMRHv3Vrkf_text","label":"ggMRHv3Vrkf_text","default":"Because the actual method is too simple. Too cheap. And it would put half the shoulder surgeons in Beverly Hills out of business."},{"type":"html","id":"ggJq9oxFPee_text","label":"ggJq9oxFPee_text","default":"You can't patent blood flow restoration."},{"type":"html","id":"ggLK-z_sBG0_text","label":"ggLK-z_sBG0_text","default":"You can't bill insurance for teaching someone how to finally get relief for their own shoulder."},{"type":"html","id":"ggxOWC-uz5O_text","label":"ggxOWC-uz5O_text","default":"<strong>Think about it:</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaU3E339jm_text","label":"ggaU3E339jm_text","default":"You wouldn't scrape the rust off a hinge and call it \"fixed.\""},{"type":"html","id":"ggwRTH7Owr7_text","label":"ggwRTH7Owr7_text","default":"You'd oil it. Lubricate it. Restore what it needs to function."},{"type":"html","id":"ggwz4oz_qlV_text","label":"ggwz4oz_qlV_text","default":"But that's exactly what invasive procedures do - scrape away the \"damage\" (tears and bone spurs) while ignoring why it formed in the first place."},{"type":"html","id":"gg9g6S4sRYb_text","label":"gg9g6S4sRYb_text","default":"So they keep you on the hamster wheel."},{"type":"html","id":"ggYRr5f3iuR_text","label":"ggYRr5f3iuR_text","default":"It's genius, really."},{"type":"html","id":"ggBzNGQlXsB_text","label":"ggBzNGQlXsB_text","default":"If you're a sociopathic medical executive who sees human suffering as a revenue stream."},{"type":"html","id":"ggxmcO-WJKz_text","label":"ggxmcO-WJKz_text","default":"<strong>THE 12-MINUTE MIRACLE HIDING IN PLAIN SIGHT</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcpYEF56H__youtubeUrl","label":"ggcpYEF56H__youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcpYEF56H__vimeoUrl","label":"ggcpYEF56H__vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/1095883398"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcpYEF56H__html5Url","label":"ggcpYEF56H__html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/270aa1c713be41d4b8551e73b3e3ae73.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSm3NaNuyn_text","label":"ggSm3NaNuyn_text","default":"Why?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOKnTr7Oi4_text","label":"ggOKnTr7Oi4_text","default":"Three weeks after my discovery, she was back at work. Full shifts in the ER."},{"type":"html","id":"gg7lDaBKycS_text","label":"gg7lDaBKycS_text","default":"Truly life-changing."},{"type":"html","id":"ggdkKDhH9xE_text","label":"ggdkKDhH9xE_text","default":"Just 12 minutes a day of something so stupidly simple, I'm embarrassed it took me 23 years of career to figure it out."},{"type":"html","id":"gghIbg238Qz_text","label":"gghIbg238Qz_text","default":"To relieve rotator cuff pain, you need to do THREE things simultaneously:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXynpdKBvr_text","label":"ggXynpdKBvr_text","default":"<strong>1. HEAT</strong> - Open the blood vessels so circulation can reach starved tissue"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCq5nRtJ2Q_text","label":"ggCq5nRtJ2Q_text","default":"<strong>2. COMPRESS</strong> - Force fresh blood and nutrients through the joint"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxrdVYOyak_text","label":"ggxrdVYOyak_text","default":"<strong>3. VIBRATE </strong>- Stimulate cellular regeneration and muscle reset"},{"type":"html","id":"ggObdU2dNU6_text","label":"ggObdU2dNU6_text","default":"Miss even ONE of these steps, and you're wasting your time."},{"type":"html","id":"ggHfFyU0Rxk_text","label":"ggHfFyU0Rxk_text","default":"That's why the usual methods don't work. (No circulation boost)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdzK3xd9FA_text","label":"ggdzK3xd9FA_text","default":"That's why massage doesn't work. (No deep tissue penetration)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbVaxXGblr_text","label":"ggbVaxXGblr_text","default":"That's why stretching doesn't work. (No cellular stimulation)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggK5RTx1zoI_text","label":"ggK5RTx1zoI_text","default":"<strong>You need all three. At the same time. In the right sequence.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYjCyL0kAN_text","label":"ggYjCyL0kAN_text","default":"A Triple Method Revival."},{"type":"html","id":"ggHcitnFDB3_text","label":"ggHcitnFDB3_text","default":"And that's exactly what I figured out how to do."}],
